com.google.api.client.googleapis.auth.oauth2

Class GoogleIdToken.Payload

  • java.lang.Object
    • IdToken.Payload
      • com.google.api.client.googleapis.auth.oauth2.GoogleIdToken.Payload
  • Enclosing class:
    GoogleIdToken

    public static class GoogleIdToken.Payload
extends IdToken.Payload
    Beta
    Google ID token payload.

    Upgrade warning: in prior version 1.15 #getAccessTokenHash() and setAccessTokenHash(String) accessed "token_hash", but starting with version 1.16 they now access "at_hash".
